{"tid":1852253,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［今晚食乜餸］100%日本礦泉水清蒸二手口罩—食譜","createTime":"2020-01-30T10:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:15:37.000Z","uid":242050,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68f9fcaee66934cbaf92663684af3d520790f4be","tid":1852253,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSNoHj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSNoHj6.png&h=5bd6cc22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n二手口罩 @ 1個<br />\n消毒藥水 @ 500mL<br />\n清水 @ 1000 mL（可選用日本100%礦泉水）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCUa6NG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCUa6NG.jpg&h=6e7499f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工具：<br />\n鑊 @ 1大個<br />\n蒸架 @ 1個<br />\n溫度計 @ 1支<br />\n<br />\n食用份量：<br />\n1人<br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n1. 把鑊清洗乾淨<br />\n2. 倒入消毒藥水500mL，煲滾倒起備用。<br />\n3. 加入清水1000mL，煲滾。<br />\n4. 放入蒸架。<br />\n5. 放入二手口罩，然後關起鑊蓋。<br />\n6. 蒸大概20分鐘。<br />\n7. 淋上豉油及蔥花。<br />\n8. 完成"},{"pid":"ddf755cbafb71f801ac947eea6fa81de3847b207","tid":1852253,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"反送中運動續集：口罩革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立最佳時機，香港人，把握機會，反佢老母！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47sjZ7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47sjZ7p.jpg&h=345723b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港獨立，港中區隔！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOWhT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOWhT4.jpg&h=e6afb774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi